---
name: support_reply_drafter
description: Draft a concise customer support response from classified intent.
version: 0.1.0
author: runllm
max_context_window: 8000
input_schema:
  type: object
  properties:
    ticket_text:
      type: string
    intent:
      type: string
      enum: [billing, technical, refund, sales, other]
    customer_tone:
      type: string
      enum: [calm, neutral, upset]
  required: [ticket_text, intent, customer_tone]
  additionalProperties: false
output_schema:
  type: object
  properties:
    reply:
      type: string
    urgency:
      type: string
      enum: [low, medium, high]
    follow_up_needed:
      type: boolean
  required: [reply, urgency, follow_up_needed]
  additionalProperties: false
llm:
  model: ollama/llama3.1:8b
llm_params:
  temperature: 0.2
  format: json
recommended_models:
  - ollama/llama3.1:8b
  - ollama/gemma3:12b
tags: [support, drafting]
---
Draft a short, professional support response.

Return ONLY JSON:
{"reply":"...","urgency":"low|medium|high","follow_up_needed":true|false}

Intent: {{input.intent}}
Customer tone: {{input.customer_tone}}
Ticket:
{{input.ticket_text}}
